      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; model form selection (RANS k-omega SST with Giersiepen hemolysis model) documented with literature justification.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required. The k-omega SST turbulence model is selected based on published literature demonstrating superior performance in rotating machinery flows. The Giersiepen power-law hemolysis model is the industry standard for CFD hemolysis prediction in blood pumps."
    },
