      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal model input uncertainty propagation is not required. All input parameters (fluid density 1056 kg/m³, Quemada viscosity coefficients, Giersiepen hemolysis constants C = 3.62e-7, alpha = 2.416, beta = 0.785) are documented with literature sources. Sensitivity to input variation is noted as a future MRL 3 activity."
