    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Validation results demonstrate NIH prediction error of 8.3 % mean relative error across all operating points, satisfying the 15 % acceptance criterion. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is met for the worst-case geometry variant. The credibility evidence package is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device tolerance analysis.",
